	<ThingDef ParentName="BaseWeaponJokeRanged">
		<defName>Joke_FlameThrower</defName>
		<label>flame thrower</label>
		<description>A glove infused with Jokium and Chemfuel that allows the wearer to toss fireballs right at an enemy. These balls of flame are volatile and explode on impact, leaving flames in the blast zone. Often used to defeat turtles and legged mushrooms.</description>
